import React from 'react'; import './Inova.css'; import ssa from './bgImages/ssa.png'; import story1 from './bgImages/story1.png'; import story2 from './bgImages/story2.png'; import item1 from './bgImages/item1.png'; import item2 from './bgImages/item2.png'; import contact from './bgImages/contact.png'; import footer from './bgImages/footer.png'; import faq from './bgImages/faq.png'; import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { faHome } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; import { Footer } from './Footer'; export function Inova() { return ( <>

Inova Game

a responsive landing page brochure focused on a pleasing front end UI/UX design

Demo

the demo is hosted free by heroku, it might take a little bit longer to load

Features

  • parallax scrolling

  • auto detect scroll section

  • google map search with marker

  • nav bar hide on scroll down, show on scroll up

  • infinite scrolling banner

  • breathable web lottie animation

  • gradient fill with svg and linear gradient

  • auto play carousel with manual control and visible animation timer

Explore More at Github
